org.magicdgs.readtools.engine

Class RTDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.magicdgs.readtools.engine.RTDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<org.broadinstitute.hellbender.utils.read.GATKRead>, org.broadinstitute.hellbender.engine.GATKDataSource<org.broadinstitute.hellbender.utils.read.GATKRead>

    public final class RTDataSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.broadinstitute.hellbender.engine.GATKDataSource<org.broadinstitute.hellbender.utils.read.GATKRead>, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    ReadTools abstract implementation of GATKDataSource for GATKRead, which includes: - Tracking the original quality encoding of the data source. - Iterates over reads already in standard format. WARNING: query is not working yet.
